room_title: Escape room "The Basement of Horror" by The Rooms of BCS in College Station
room_description: You have a very odd neighbor. Often you see him bringing garbage bags to his car and driving off with them the same time every day for an hour. This particular day you and your friends decide to investigate your neighbor's house and sneak in through the basement. Unfortunately, you find yourself locked in! You have only one hour to escape before you become his next victim!
